# Backup dump artifacts (NFR-08, D-72/D-73, T-05-03-DUMPLEAK): pg_dump -Fc snapshots +
# mirrored MinIO objects contain ciphertext + KEK-adjacent PII and must NEVER enter VCS.
# The `backup` compose service uses a named Docker volume (never a repo bind mount) —
# this entry is defense-in-depth in case a local/manual `docker cp` extraction or a
# future bind-mount lands one under the repo root.
backups/
